	<div class="entry-details">
				<p>
			<a href="http://ianmilligan.ca/2013/05/10/an-aside-an-ode-to-exploratory-research/" title="4:57 pm" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-05-10T16:57:23+00:00" pubdate>10 May 2013</time></a><br/><span class="byline"> by <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://ianmilligan.ca/author/ianmilligan1/" title="View all posts by Ian Milligan" rel="author">Ian Milligan</a></span></span>							<a href="http://ianmilligan.ca/2013/05/10/an-aside-an-ode-to-exploratory-research/#respond" title="Comment on An Aside: An Ode to Exploratory&nbsp;Research">Leave a comment</a>					</p>
